msIdentifier.repository: Kislak Center for Special Collections, Rare Books and Manuscripts

msContents.summary: Lecture notes on scholastic philosophy, comprising commentaries on two works by Aristotle and a work on metaphysics concerning the concept of being (ratio entis), the distinction between essence and existence, and real, formal, and virtual distinctions.
